---

<section id="about">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <p class="section-label">About</p>

    <h1 style="
      font-size: clamp(36px, 5vw, 64px);
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      line-height: 1.05;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    ">
      Neuroscientist studying the sleeping brain.
    </h1>

    <p style="margin: 0 0 1em; color: var(--color-fg);">
      I am a Research Fellow at the National Institute of Neurological Disorders and Stroke (NINDS),
      NIH, working with Dr. Jeff Duyn. My research uses whole-brain functional MRI to understand
      the neuroscience of sleep — from data-driven characterization of sleep stages to how sleep
      shapes adolescent brain development, cognition, and mental health.
    </p>
    <p style="margin: 0 0 1.75em; color: var(--color-secondary);">
      My work has appeared in <em>The Lancet Child &amp; Adolescent Health</em>, <em>eLife</em>,
      <em>Sleep</em>, <em>NeuroImage</em>, and <em>The Washington Post</em>.
      A single study on adolescent sleep earned an Altmetric score of 2,511 and 200+ news mentions.
    </p>

    <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.75rem; margin-bottom: 3rem;">
      <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get in Touch</a>
      <a href="/CV_NilsYang04212026.pdf" target="_blank" class="btn btn-outline">Download CV</a>
      <a
        href="https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=sHvN8soAAAAJ&hl=en"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="btn btn-outline"
      >
        Google Scholar
      </a>
    </div>

    <hr class="divider" style="margin-bottom: 2rem;" />

    <!-- At-a-glance grid -->
    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem;">
      <div>
        <p class="section-label" style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Position</p>
        <p style="margin: 0; font-weight: 600; font-size: clamp(15px, 1.3vw, 17px);">Research Fellow</p>
        <p style="margin: 0; color: var(--color-secondary); font-size: 14px;">NINDS, NIH · 2023–present</p>
        <p style="margin: 0.25rem 0 0; color: var(--color-secondary); font-size: 14px;">Advisor: Jeff Duyn</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="section-label" style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Education</p>
        <p style="margin: 0; font-weight: 600; font-size: clamp(15px, 1.3vw, 17px);">Ph.D., Cognitive Neuroscience</p>
        <p style="margin: 0; color: var(--color-secondary); font-size: 14px;">Sun Yat-Sen University, 2018</p>
        <p style="margin: 0.25rem 0 0; color: var(--color-secondary); font-size: 14px;">Visiting PhD, UPenn (2015–2018)</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="section-label" style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Recognition</p>
        <p style="margin: 0; font-weight: 600; font-size: clamp(15px, 1.3vw, 17px);">Trainee Merit Reward</p>
        <p style="margin: 0; color: var(--color-secondary); font-size: 14px;">Sleep Meeting 2024</p>
        <p style="margin: 0.25rem 0 0; color: var(--color-secondary); font-size: 14px;">Performance Cash Award, NINDS</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="section-label" style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Research Focus</p>
        <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.4rem;">
          {['Sleep fMRI', 'Brain Connectivity', 'Adolescent Dev.', 'ASL/CBF'].map((tag) => (
            <span class="tag">{tag}</span>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
